			<br /><b>2. KSHITIJ</b> (the annual Techno-Management Fest)<br /><br />Now lets come to our techfest Kshitij(KTJ). Kshitij receives overwhelming participation from the student community all over the world. The official website of Kshitij, ktj.in, is in fact the largest student run website, receiving 8 million clicks in its 2012 edition. Do you know that KTJ is Asia's LARGEST TECHNO-MANAGEMENT fest!?Well, now you know. KTJ hosts a plethora of technological competitions, events and guest lectures and performances from renowned celebs and tech-gurus. World renowned organizations like ACM, IEEE, ASME, ASHRAE and IMechE certify numerous events of the fest. In brief, KTJ is a great opportunity to have fun alongside great learning and composing ever-lasting memories...<br>
