		<li><h4>GENERAL CHAMPIONSHIP (GC)</h4>
		<center><a><img src="../pics/cup.jpg" style="width:50%;"></a></center>
			As the name suggest it is the annual inter hall competition between diff. halls in IIT KGP. It has three different fields : Sports, Technology and So-cult(social & culture). Its the time when ur hall tempo will be at its peak. Each and every boarder of that hall takes part in it whether they will be in team or in cheering team. It is the best time to show your talent and dedication. There are so many diff events under GC. Each event has points. Finally the hall with most points in a category gets the trophy of that GC. If a hall wins all 3 GCs then its called<b> "Platinum GC"</b>.
